  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Add Statistics FB</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" style="page-break-before:always;">Why use a Statistics FB?</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Statistical data<text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> may include values as RMS , Maximum, Minimum, etc. values of a variable (wire data-channel). </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Use a <text styleclass="Element">Statistics FB</text> to list the <text styleclass="VariableName">Statistical data</text> for the data that is available at the output of a different <text styleclass="VariableName">Function-Block.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See also : <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-Statistics">Statistics dialog</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Add Statistics FB</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="3" colcount="3">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:100px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-align:right;">What to do : </para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-align:right;"></para>
        </td>
        <td colspan="2">
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Add a Statistics FB to the graphic-area </li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="2" colcount="2">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:41px;">
                <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-align:right;"><image src="MD-Icon-FB-Stats.png" scale="100.00%" padding="0 2 0 0" figurelistinclude="0"><title>Add Statistics FB</title></image></para>
              </td>
              <td>
                <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click </text><text styleclass="T_Menu">Add menu &gt; Add Statistics FB</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Interface2">OR</para>
                <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click</text><text styleclass="Interface">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Menu-FB-Modelling" styleclass="T_Menu">Modeling FB toolbar</link><text styleclass="T_Menu"> &gt; Add Statistics FB</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td colspan="2" style="vertical-align:middle;">
                <para styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text">Then:</text></para>
                <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click the graphic-area</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="Element">Statistic FB</text> is now in the<text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text">graphic-area</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2" style="width:120px;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-GA-StatsFB.ipp" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Connect a wire to its input-connector</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="5" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text style="font-style:normal;">Drag a wire from a different </text><text styleclass="Element">FB</text><text style="font-style:normal;"> to the input-connector of the </text><text styleclass="Element">Statistics FB</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">A wire is now connected to the input-connector of the <text styleclass="Element">Statistics FB</text>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="3">
          <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="3" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Open the Statistics dialog</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="7" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text">Double-click a </text><text styleclass="Element">Statistics FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> in the graphic-area</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Interface2">OR</para>
